00:00:05,000 --> 00:02:11,000
Kobo Baby Party! #Kobo3rdAnniversary

3
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:25,500
Cerah sekali hari ini.
It's so bright today.

4
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:30,000
Yah, langit yang sangat biru.
Yeah, a very blue sky.

5
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,500
Langit biru, membara hati.
Blue sky, burning heart.

6
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:42,000
Putih awan, setulus cintaku pun bersemi.
White clouds, as sincere as my love blooming.

7
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:44,500
Ini kurang kece nih.
This is not cool enough.

8
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,500
Hah, bentar.
Hah, wait.

9
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:50,000
Kita baca chat dulu ya guys, kita absen dulu ya.
Let's read the chat first guys, let's do a roll call.

10
00:02:50,500 --> 00:02:54,000
Bo intro bo intro... eh, saya bukan Kobo ya.
Bo intro bo intro... eh, I'm not Kobo.

11
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,500
Panggil aku Ceboo.
Call me Ceboo.

12
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,000
Ya sama-sama bo sih.
Well, both are "bo".

13
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:03,500
Tapi di sini saya bukan Kobo ya, tapi...
But here I'm not Kobo, but...

14
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:04,500
oke, intro dulu ya guys.
okay, intro first guys.

15
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:08,500
Bocebocebo, Cebokan Nairu siap menghujani hatimu
Bocebocebo, Cebokan Nairu is ready to rain on your heart

16
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:12,000
dengan petir cintaku.
with my lightning of love.

17
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,500
Anjis. Oke, mari kita lihat live chat lagi.
Damn. Okay, let's look at the live chat again.

18
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,500
Kak itu ada gitar di belakang, coba mainin dong.
Kak, there's a guitar behind you, try playing it.

19
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:24,000
mendengar Kak Cebo bernyanyi.
hear Kak Cebo sing.

20
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:27,500
Wiya, ada gitar ya? Oh.
Wiya, there's a guitar? Oh.

21
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,500
There's guitar here. Sodesune.
There's a guitar here. That's right.

22
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:34,000
Tapi gimana ya, aku gak pandai nyanyi guys.
But how, I'm not good at singing guys.

23
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:38,000
suara Kakak ganteng banget pasti bagus kalau nyanyi.
your voice is so handsome, it must be good if you sing.

24
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:41,000
Aduh, iya iya. Ya udahlah shoganai wa.
Gosh, okay okay. Well then, it can't be helped.

25
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:46,500
Tapi satu lagu aja ya, okay only one song okay.
But just one song, okay only one song okay.

26
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:50,000
Maaf ya guys kalau sedikit gimana gitu,
Sorry guys if it's a bit like that,

27
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,500
soalnya aku emang gak pandai nyanyi.
because I'm really not good at singing.

28
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,000
Ya udah, let's go.
Well then, let's go.

29
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:03,000
星みたいに隠れて
Hiding like a star,

30
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:07,000
終わらないピントで
with an endless focus...

31
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:08,500
HELP!!

32
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:13,200
天使はもうこの部屋にはいない
The angel is no longer in this room.

33
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:17,500
顔も知らない人達と
With people whose faces I don't know,

34
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:21,000
目が合う今日この頃
our eyes meet these days.

35
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:24,000
何かを指針にして
Using something as a guide,

36
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:30,500
動き始める歯車
the gears start to move.

37
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:37,500
私の耳を劈くような音
A sound that seems to pierce my ears,

38
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:40,800
いらない物ねだり
