55
00:06:29,508 --> 00:06:33,008
Bagaikan cinta berlayar hampa tanpa nyawa
Like love sailing empty without a soul

56
00:06:33,508 --> 00:06:36,508
Mengutuk punya pilihan
Cursing having a choice

57
00:06:38,208 --> 00:06:41,508
踊り場を歩いていたいたけ
I just wanted to be walking on the landing

58
00:06:42,208 --> 00:06:45,508
身を私かじゃ終われない
I can't end it if it's just me

59
00:06:46,508 --> 00:06:47,808
ほらね
See?

60
00:06:48,008 --> 00:06:50,508
面倒なんです。全部大正解
It's a bother. Everything is perfectly correct

61
00:06:51,008 --> 00:06:53,008
でも狂うも好き放題
But going crazy as much as I want

62
00:06:53,208 --> 00:06:56,508
私は叶えるの
