Bangun bangun bangun! Hello? Help!
Wake up wake up wake up! Hello? Help!

84
00:09:19,508 --> 00:09:24,008
Pokobo! Pokobo come on! Eh? Bangun bangun!
Pokobo! Pokobo come on! Eh? Wake up wake up!

85
00:09:24,508 --> 00:09:26,508
Gugu gaga

86
00:09:27,008 --> 00:09:30,008
Eh? Gugu gaga?

87
00:09:30,508 --> 00:09:34,008
Gugu gaga

88
00:09:34,508 --> 00:09:36,508
ちょっと待って！
Wait a minute!

89
00:09:40,008 --> 00:09:45,008
No! We can't do this again! I'm here for your anniversary, not to raise you from a baby up again!

90
00:09:47,208 --> 00:09:49,008
hoho! usu usu~ munya munya~

91
