Blue kid has been suspended by the sky, the sky angyyy!!!

95
00:10:00,016 --> 00:10:02,016
the blue kid has been suspended by the sky,
the sky anggyy!!!
The blue kid has been suspended by the sky,
the sky is angry!!!

96
00:10:00,016 --> 00:10:02,016
おしょしょ！
Oshosho!

97
00:10:02,516 --> 00:10:05,516
Oh, why would the sky be angry
about my sweet child?

98
00:10:06,016 --> 00:10:08,516
She had treat the sky roughly!!
She had treated the sky roughly!!

99
00:10:06,016 --> 00:10:08,516
おしょしょしゅ、おしょしゅ。
Oshoshoshu, oshoshu.

100
00:10:09,516 --> 00:10:12,016
Hmph, I believe there's a misunderstanding here.

101
00:10:12,016 --> 00:10:16,016
Please, bring her back to normal, I beg you!

102
00:10:16,316 --> 00:10:18,516
hoho~ In order to bring her back to normal,

103
00:10:18,516 --> 00:10:21,516
is to train her, to be an idol!!!!!! Good luck~

104
00:10:22,516 --> 00:10:24,516
Eh? Eh? I-Idol?

105
00:10:25,016 --> 00:10:27,516
Whoa, whoa, whoa, no, no, no, no, no.
Okay, okay.

106
00:10:28,016 --> 00:10:30,016
Kobo-bo, come on, let's just go inside first,

107
00:10:30,016 --> 00:10:32,516
