108
00:10:34,016 --> 00:10:36,516
んぐぐあぐあ...
Ngugu agwa...

109
00:10:38,016 --> 00:10:41,016
Can you stand up and walk normally?

110
00:10:41,016 --> 00:10:43,016
I know you can.

111
00:10:44,016 --> 00:10:46,516
Gonna try, try. Here, here, here.

112
00:10:46,516 --> 00:10:49,016
You've done this before, many years ago.

113
00:10:49,016 --> 00:10:52,016
All right, there you go!

114
00:10:52,016 --> 00:10:54,016
あー！
Aaah!

115
00:10:54,516 --> 00:10:56,516
Oh no! Are you okay?

116
00:11:03,516 --> 00:11:06,016
Okay, okay. You know what? If you 頑張る
Okay, okay. You know what? If you work hard

117
00:11:06,016 --> 00:11:08,516
and do your best to walk on your own,

118
00:11:08,516 --> 00:11:10,516
