119
00:11:14,016 --> 00:11:15,516
Ah...

120
00:11:15,516 --> 00:11:17,516
Kusogaki, not again.
You little brat, not again.

121
00:11:31,016 --> 00:11:33,016
And here we are back!

122
00:11:43,016 --> 00:11:45,016
Wait, Biboo?

123
00:12:24,016 --> 00:12:28,016
Attention! Attention! I-I-Attention, please!

124
00:12:28,516 --> 00:12:31,516
Time for your first lesson, because

125
00:12:31,516 --> 00:12:33,516
apparently we're here with a lot of kids,

126
00:12:34,016 --> 00:12:36,016
but I think I would like some

127
00:12:36,016 --> 00:12:38,516
