128
00:12:39,516 --> 00:12:43,016
Let's begin with... hmm, you?

129
00:12:44,016 --> 00:12:46,016
Tell me your name.

130
00:12:47,016 --> 00:12:50,016
あ-い-び-び... よっぴ！
A-I-B-B... Yoppi!

131
00:12:50,016 --> 00:12:51,516
Ha! Yoppi-yoppi!

132
00:13:00,016 --> 00:13:02,016
Your name is Yoppi? Yoppi? Okay.

133
00:13:02,016 --> 00:13:06,016
Very good, Biboo! Okay.

134
00:13:08,516 --> 00:13:11,516
I go next to you. Who are you? Hmm?

135
00:13:12,016 --> 00:13:14,016
Introduction!

136
00:13:15,016 --> 00:13:20,516
び-び-わ-わ... べいぶ！
B-B-W-W... Beibu!

137
00:13:21,016 --> 00:13:25,516
Okay, good job! Beibu! Thank you!

138
00:13:27,516 --> 00:13:30,016
Who are you, cutie-patootie? Hmm?

139
00:13:31,016 --> 00:13:37,016
んまま、んまま、んまま、ふわぁー！
Mm-mama, mm-mama, mm-mama, Fuwaaa!

140
00:13:39,016 --> 00:13:42,016
Okay, okay! And now...

141
00:13:44,516 --> 00:13:47,516
Because I seem to not be able to recognize

142
00:13:47,516 --> 00:13:50,016
