143
00:14:00,016 --> 00:14:03,016
こ-ぼ-ば！
Ko-bo-ba!

144
00:14:04,016 --> 00:14:07,016
Okay, I guess it was Kobo after all.
Good job everybody! Well done!

145
00:14:07,016 --> 00:14:10,016
You did so well!

146
00:14:11,016 --> 00:14:14,016
Kobo, do you remember who I am?

147
00:14:15,016 --> 00:14:18,516
ママ！ママ！ママ！ママ！
Mama! Mama! Mama! Mama!

148
00:14:19,016 --> 00:14:22,016
Yes, Mama! But also known as Takanashi Kiara

149
00:14:22,016 --> 00:14:25,016
from Hololive English Myth!

150
00:14:25,516 --> 00:14:30,016
And today I seem to be the babysitter
of this group.

151
00:14:33,516 --> 00:14:36,016
But, but, but, ちょっと待って。
But, but, but, wait a minute.

152
00:14:36,016 --> 00:14:38,516
Why are these babies here anyway?
What's going on?

153
00:14:40,016 --> 00:14:42,516
hoho! usu usu~ munyamunya~

154
00:14:43,016 --> 00:14:46,016
I thought I made only Kobo into a baby

155
00:14:46,016 --> 00:14:49,016
it seems that all the girls on this island
have become babies!

156
00:14:55,516 --> 00:14:58,516
Kiara, I asked you to babysit!

157
00:15:00,024 --> 00:15:02,324
キアラ、子守り頼んだよ〜
Kiara, I asked you to babysit!

158
00:15:02,524 --> 00:15:03,524
Did you understand?

159
00:15:03,524 --> 00:15:05,524
わかった！ わかった！
Understood! Understood!

160
00:15:09,524 --> 00:15:14,324
Okay! Doesn't matter. Everybody, I think we should play a game, yeah?

161
00:15:18,024 --> 00:15:23,524
Okay! No problem. I have an idea. We're gonna draw something over there.

162
00:15:23,524 --> 00:15:28,524
I'm gonna draw something, and you all will guess what it is!

163
00:15:29,024 --> 00:15:30,024
ばば？
Baba?

164
00:15:30,524 --> 00:15:34,524
Yeah! And if you get it right, you'll get a big cake! How about that?

165
00:15:44,724 --> 00:15:46,324
Are you ready?

166
00:15:46,324 --> 00:15:48,024
Yes! Babu!

167
00:15:49,024 --> 00:15:51,524
Okay! We'll start with round one!

168
00:15:53,824 --> 00:15:57,024
While I draw, you will behave! いい子にしてね〜
While I draw, you will behave! Be good babies, okay?

169
00:16:19,024 --> 00:16:21,024
座って！ ここに、座って、座って、座って！
Sit down! Sit here, sit, sit, sit!

170
00:16:23,024 --> 00:16:26,524
It's finished! Everybody, please take a look! 見て見て！
It's finished! Everybody, please take a look! Look, look!

171
00:16:29,324 --> 00:16:31,524
What is this? What is this thing?

172
00:16:38,024 --> 00:16:40,524
これは、何でしょう？
What is this, I wonder?

173
00:16:48,524 --> 00:16:53,024
にゃ？ ねこ？ 猫？ Cat! Cat!
Nya? Neko? Cat! Cat! Cat!

174
00:16:54,024 --> 00:16:59,024
Maybe! Potential answer. もしかしたら、そうかもしれないけど...
Maybe! Potential answer. It might be that, but...

175
00:17:00,024 --> 00:17:02,524
What does Yopi-chan think that this is?
What does Yopi-chan think this is?

176
00:17:03,024 --> 00:17:05,524
かば？ かば！
Hippo? Hippo!

177
00:17:06,024 --> 00:17:11,024
こぼ！ こぼ！ こぼ！
Kobo! Kobo! Kobo!

178
00:17:15,524 --> 00:17:18,524
I don't think so... But we will see! We will see!

179
00:17:20,024 --> 00:17:22,524
Biboo-chan! What do you think that is over there?

180
00:17:23,024 --> 00:17:25,024
うんち！
Poop!

181
00:17:26,824 --> 00:17:31,524
え？ Is my drawing that bad? そんなにひどい？
What? Is my drawing that bad? Is it that bad?

182
00:17:33,024 --> 00:17:37,024
Abugo-bo! Not unchi, what is this? Tell me!
Abugo-bo! It's not poop, what is this? Tell me!

183
00:17:41,024 --> 00:17:47,024
いん... いんご... いんご... いぬ！
Do... Do... Do... Dog!

184
00:17:48,024 --> 00:17:51,524
いぬ？ りんご？ りんご？
Dog? Apple? Apple?

185
00:17:53,524 --> 00:17:57,024
Yes! いぬ！ 正解！
Yes! Dog! Correct!

186
00:18:04,024 --> 00:18:07,524
Okay! Round two! Start time!

187
00:18:09,024 --> 00:18:13,024
Please behave, okay? シー... スタート！
Please behave, okay? Shh... Start!

188
00:18:45,024 --> 00:18:48,024
じゃじゃ！ Look at this!
Ta-da! Look at this!

189
00:18:50,524 --> 00:18:54,524
