770
01:00:13,096 --> 01:00:15,596
Banyak banget pelajaran yang bisa diambil dari stream ini.
There are so many lessons to be learned from this stream.

771
01:00:15,596 --> 01:00:18,596
Terima kasih ya, Bang Arsy Widianto-kun.
Thank you, Bang Arsy Widianto-kun.

772
01:00:18,896 --> 01:00:22,896
Aku juga berterima kasih banget. Aku happy banget.
I'm also very grateful. I'm so happy.

773
01:00:23,096 --> 01:00:25,596
Jadi, aku lanjut ya.
So, I'll be going now.

774
01:00:27,596 --> 01:00:30,096
Ni nggak nggak ilfeel kan diundang ama anime ya?
You're not turned off by being invited by an anime, right?

775
01:00:30,096 --> 01:00:31,096
Enggak lah.
No way.

776
01:00:31,096 --> 01:00:32,096
Enggak ya?
Really?

777
01:00:32,096 --> 01:00:34,596
Ya kalau buat kamu mah apa sih yang enggak.
For you, I'd do anything.

778
01:00:34,596 --> 01:00:36,096
Udahlah, tenang aja.
Don't worry about it.

779
01:00:36,596 --> 01:00:41,096
Eh ayo kita kita kayak... Coba coba di-pet-pet bisa nggak kita?
Hey, let's... Can you try to give me head pats?

780
01:00:43,896 --> 01:00:45,896
Kok kayaknya pendek banget sih aku?
Why do I look so short?

781
01:00:45,896 --> 01:00:49,096
Kayaknya aku nggak sependek ini deh harusnya. Ha? Ha?
I shouldn't be this short. Huh? Huh?

782
01:00:51,096 --> 01:00:54,096
Ha? Ha? Ha? Buset, sombongnya! Parah banget.
Huh? Huh? Huh? Geez, how arrogant! That's too much.

783
01:00:54,596 --> 01:00:57,096
Eh kita kita fist bump fist bump fist bump.
Hey, let's do a fist bump.

784
01:00:57,096 --> 01:00:58,296
Oke, fist bump.
Okay, fist bump.

785
01:01:03,596 --> 01:01:05,596
High five! High five!

786
01:01:08,596 --> 01:01:10,296
Ya udah deh.
Alright then.

787
01:01:10,296 --> 01:01:14,296
Oke, baiklah. Terima kasih banyak sekali lagi, Kobo. Makasih banget.
Okay, then. Thank you so much once again, Kobo. Thanks a lot.

788
01:01:15,596 --> 01:01:19,596
Jangan ke mana-mana, ikut ini nggak? Makan-makan dulu kita.
Don't go yet, want to join? Let's go eat first.

789
01:01:19,596 --> 01:01:23,096
Boleh. Mau ke mana? Mau makan apa? Ayo.
Sure. Where to? What do you want to eat? Let's go.

790
01:01:23,096 --> 01:01:26,596
Ih buset, sok soft-spoken gini buset guys! Aaa!
Geez, he's acting all soft-spoken! Aaa!

791
01:01:26,896 --> 01:01:28,896
Ayo ayo, ya udah nanti di belakang ya.
Come on, okay, let's meet backstage then.

792
01:01:28,896 --> 01:01:30,296
Ya udah, oke.
Alright, okay.

793
01:01:30,296 --> 01:01:31,896
Ya udah, aku lanjut ya.
Okay, I'll head out.

794
01:01:31,896 --> 01:01:33,296
Istirahat dulu ya?
Taking a break?

795
01:01:33,296 --> 01:01:35,296
Iya. Kamu jangan capek-capek juga ya.
Yeah. You don't overwork yourself either.

796
01:01:35,296 --> 01:01:36,896
Oke, iya iya. Makasih. Dah.
Okay, yeah, thanks. Bye.

797
01:01:36,896 --> 01:01:38,096
Arigato. Dah dah.
Thanks. Bye bye.

798
01:01:38,096 --> 01:01:39,596
Mata ne. Dah.
See you. Bye.

799
01:01:39,596 --> 01:01:42,596
Eh iya Cirus-ga dah. Iya dianterin sana.
Oh right, bye Cirus. Yes, take him there.

800
01:01:46,596 --> 01:01:49,096
もう終わりましたかな？
Is it already over?

801
01:01:51,896 --> 01:01:53,896
Hee, yattai!
Yay, I did it!

802
01:01:54,096 --> 01:01:57,596
Iya, yukkuri shitai.
Yeah, I want to take it slow.

803
01:01:58,596 --> 01:02:02,096
Jadi gimana surprise-nya? Kalian suka nggak?
So, how was the surprise? Did you guys like it?

804
01:02:03,596 --> 01:02:05,596
Eh! Cirus!

805
01:02:05,596 --> 01:02:09,596
Cirus, ini dia yang akan kita obrol nanti guys!
Cirus, this is what we'll talk about later, guys!

806
01:02:09,596 --> 01:02:13,596
Kawaii, kamu nanti bakal dijual banyak ya Cirus ya?
So cute, you'll be sold a lot, right Cirus?

807
01:02:13,896 --> 01:02:16,896
You will be... You will be sold...

808
01:02:16,896 --> 01:02:20,596
by many many customers, so...

809
01:02:20,596 --> 01:02:24,596
please be a good Cirus. Hehe.

810
01:02:25,596 --> 01:02:27,896
Kalau gitu kita beneran closing-nya!
Then, let's really do the closing!

811
01:02:28,296 --> 01:02:32,096
Semoga kalian seneng sama surprise itu,
I hope you liked that surprise,

812
01:02:32,096 --> 01:02:35,596
performance tadi, eh!
and the performance just now!

813
01:02:36,596 --> 01:02:41,596
Bokoboko, Kobo Kanaeru at your service.

814
01:02:41,596 --> 01:02:44,296
Let me be your sun to shine your day. Ehe!

815
01:02:44,296 --> 01:02:47,096
Bye bye semuanya! Terima kasih! Bye bye!
Bye bye everyone! Thank you! Bye bye!

816
01:02:59,596 --> 01:03:00,896
Chape.
I'm tired.

817
01:03:01,096 --> 01:03:02,296
Chape!
Tired!

818
01:03:02,296 --> 01:03:04,896
もう終わりだ！
It's finally over!

819
01:04:20,096 --> 01:04:21,296
Say Dada.

820
01:04:21,296 --> 01:04:22,596
Dada!

821
01:05:00,104 --> 01:05:02,604
星みたいに隠れて、合わないピント
Hiding like a star, focus is lost

822
01:05:02,904 --> 01:05:05,204
天使は、もうこの部屋にはいない
The angel is no longer in this room

823
01:05:05,504 --> 01:05:07,804
顔も知らない人と目が合う、今日この頃
Meeting eyes with strangers, these days

824
01:05:08,104 --> 01:05:11,304
何かを指針にして、動き始める歯車
Guided by something, the gears start moving

825
01:05:11,604 --> 01:05:13,204
私の耳を劈くような音
The sound that pierces my ears

826
01:05:13,504 --> 01:05:15,604
ないものねだりで夜が...
Wanting what I don't have, the night...

827
01:05:15,904 --> 01:05:18,504
明け始めてく、不透明なまま
begins to break, remaining opaque.

828
01:05:18,804 --> 01:05:21,004
手探りで進む、一歩、一歩
Fumbling forward, step by step,

829
01:05:21,304 --> 01:05:23,604
その先に何があるか、今はわからなくても
even if I don't know what lies ahead yet.

830
01:05:23,904 --> 01:05:26,604
信じていたい、私の歌声を
I want to believe in my own singing voice.

831
01:05:26,904 --> 01:05:30,104
誰かに届くまで、歌い続けるから
I'll keep singing until it reaches someone.

